G1 X51.00 Y3.00 Z8.00 F2000 ; Return to center after circular wipe
G0 Z20.00 ; Lift brush to z_safe_dip after wipe/shake
G0 X51.00 Y3.00 ; Return to dip center after wipe/shake (at z_safe_dip)
; --- End Dip Cycle ---
